This paper is primarily focused on mobile security and malware detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of behavior profiling and classification techniques, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of emulation and system logs, which are related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SI).
